this is the bonus stats from sets


SET GREEN COLOR RARITY 4 Peice
Set of the Wind Lord
Helm, Chest, Sword, Boots.

2 Peice bonus
increase evasion by 8%
increase Pure resist by 10%

3 Peice bonus
increase evasion by 9%
increase Pure resist by 12%
increase movespeed by 15%

4 Peice bonus
increase evasion by 10%
increase Pure resist by 15%
increase movespeed by 20%
increase attack speed by 30
reduce cast point time on spell by 25%

also give modifier to the user
Basic attack and Spell Q will do WIND DAMAGE, wind damage does 75% Physical and 25% Pure damage, spell and basic attack will have 10% chance
to Tornado the target lifting them for 1.5 second when they land, they will take 22 plus 15% of the user Primary stats into 60% physical and 
40% pure damage, Lifted units can still be damage but for 15% less damage from other people but the user of the set and others that have it



SET BLUE COLOR RARITY 3 Peice
set of the Alor Death
Sword, gloves, helm

1 Peice bonus
reduce Life regeneration source by 70%
reduce healing effect by 25%

2 Peice bonus
increase life bonus regeneration by 20%
increase armor by 10%
increase pure resist by 5%

3 Peice bonus
increase life bonus regeneration by 40%
increase armor by 10%
increase pure resist by 10%
increase life regeneration by 4.5
increase health by 225

also give modifier to the user
the user will also critical hit every 3 spell cast for 200% of the damage into Pure and making them take 15% increase damage for 4 second
and for every 5 hit done with Danudor, the User will lifesteal for 125% of the damage dealt and dealing 2.4% of the target health in bonus
pure damage 0.2% for bosses, other allys that have Alor Death Set will have bonus for every User with the Set, reducing damage taken by
7% for every ally near of 450 radius max of 14% damage reduction



SET ORANGE COLOR RARITY 4 Peice
set of the Nhantalur Will
Glove, helm, chest-armor, boots

2 peice bonus
increase armor by 3
increase life regeneration by 3.5
reduce spell amp by 7%

3 peice bonus
increase armor bonus by 6
increase life regeneration by 6.5
increase Physical Q SPELL damage by 25%
increase health by 7%
reduce spell amp by 12%

4 Peice bonus
increase armor bonus by 9
increase life regeneration by 9.5
increase Physical Q and W SPELL damage by 35%
increase health by 11%
reduce spell amp by 18%
reduce movespeed by 13%

also give a modifier to the user
all spell that you deal magical attack will have 50% reduce damage and all physical spell will deal bleeding bonus damage on the target,
dealing 24 plus 15% of strenght and agility in damage every 0.5 second for 5 second, the bleed damage will have 8% reduce damage every
tick of damage dealing less damage in return, and all magical attack taken will heal the user for 35% of the damage taken and allys
near him of 500 radius will be heal for 10% of the damage he takes, the blood damage is physical and the bleed damage cannot go lower
than dealing 9 damage per 0.5 second



SET GREEN COLOR RARITY 2 Peice
Set of the Mad Being
2-HandSword, Gloves

2 Peice bonus
increase damage by 8%
increase physical spell damage by 10%
increase all Stats by 4
reduce base attack time by 0.35

also give a modifier to the user
every attack on the same target will lower base attack time by 0.03 up to 0.30 and also increase damage by 2% up to 20% bonus as well
attacking a new target will reset the stacks, and for every stack that the user got upon switching target will do 8 physical damage
for all of those stacks on switching, bosses will take 50% increase total damage of the stacks
